Package gov.lbl.glamm.client.model

Interface Summary
AnnotatedMapData.Attribute Interface containing GLAMM-specific SVG annotations.
AnnotatedMapData.State Interface indicating the set of states an interactive map element may have.
 

Class Summary
AnnotatedMapData The annotated SVG map and associated data.
AnnotatedMapDescriptor A compact description of the satellite data associated with a GLAMM-annotated SVG map - it's effectively a data transfer object.
Cart A cart for holding ordered sets of compounds, genes, pathways, reactions, and samples, as selected by the user.
Citation Representation of an external data source's citation
Compound Representation of a Compound
Experiment Representation of an Experiment - wraps a collection of Samples with the same experiment id.
Gene Representation of a Gene
Measurement A measurement, typically associated with a sample.
MetabolicNetwork The metabolic network graph associated with a GLAMM annotated SVG map.
MetabolicNetwork.MNNode Representation of a node in a metabolic network.
Organism Model class for Organism.
Organism.OrganismComparator Comparator for listing Organism names alphabetically.
Pathway Model class for Pathways - ordered lists of reactions.
Reaction Model class for reactions.
Reaction.Participant Internal class for reaction participants.
Sample Model class for Sample - the basic unit of experimental data.
User Model class for users.
 

Enum Summary
Algorithm Enumerated type for available retrosynthesis algorithms.
AnnotatedMapData.ElementClass Enum enumerating the set of CSS classes associated with interactive map elements.
Reaction.Direction Enum specifying reaction direction.
Reaction.Participant.KeggRpairRole Enum for KEGG Rpair role.
Sample.DataType Enum for the various data types: those explicitly supported by the GLAMM database (Fitness, Protein, RNA, RNASeq) and those uploaded by the user (Session.)
Sample.TargetType Gets the target type on to which the Sample data will be projected.
